dct_title_s: Atlantic City Expressway, New Jersey map and insets
dct_description_sm: Atlantic City Expressway route map extending through Atlantic, Camden and Gloucester counties in New Jersey. Map includes insignia from the Frank S. Farley Service Plaza with listings of Holiday House Restaurant, Gulf Gasoline and Macrie Farm Market. 14 insets of the Atlantic City terminus of expressway and major interchanges.
